snippet.title: Meteor Clash Mobile Game Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Meteor Clash Mobile Game

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kpgames.meteorclash

Meteor Clash is a fun, endless casual game for all ages. Explore space through 7 unique maps of increasing difficulty avoiding meteorites and missiles. Collect coins, boosters, unlock skins and achievements and conquer the space leaderboard.

✓ Endless Games
✓ Challenging Gameplay
✓ 7 Space Maps
✓ 8 Unique Space Ships
✓ 30+ Achievements
✓ Leaderboards
